introText: I'm very passionate and dedicated to my work. and I try to be up-to-date at least in my specialty. For more than 2 years, I have been doing front-end programming with Next Js framework and React Js library.

My field of study was computer science and I realized that I am more interested in programming and it is very attractive to me. That's why from the age of 20 I started seriously I learned programming, first I started with html and css, until now I reached React and Next js and it's still going on... I try to learn new things every day and keep myself updated. And in these 2 years of work experience that the project I did things like personal site, shop, service and different panels, I got the necessary skills, knowledge and experience for the success of the projects.
